      <title>美国新屋开工率降至三个月来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-19/us-housing-starts-slide-to-lowest-level-in-three-months-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 月份，美国新屋开工量下降 3.1%，降幅为三个月以来的最低水平，而新独栋住宅开工量下降 6.9%，多户住宅开工量增长 9.6%，为三个月以来的首次增长。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-19/us-housing-starts-slide-to-lowest-level-in-three-months-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 13:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
